OL,5, Home Secretary Suella Braverman is     
OL,6, facing criticism after she said the    
OL,7, international asylum system was no     
OL,8, longer fit for purpose.                
OL,10,FIn a speech earlier, Mrs Braverman said
OL,11,Ffearing discrimination for being gay or
OL,12,Fa woman should not be enough to qualify
OL,13,Ffor refugee protection.                
OL,15,FBut the United Nations' refugee agency 
OL,16,F(UNHCR) rejected her calls for the     
OL,17,Frules to be "tightened".               
OL,19,FIt said the 1951 Refugee Convention    
OL,20,F"remains a life-saving instrument".    
